<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 dynj dwnj dqt ạ̉jrạs ạlʿyd
 dynj dwnj btqwl dh ʿyd sʿyd
 1- wmlạykẗ tqwl ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlạ̉lḥạn
 lyswʿ fạdy ạlạ̹nsạn
 dynj dh yswʿ fạdy ạlạ̹nsạn
 2- wnʿysẖ fy hnạ dh yswʿ ạ̹lh mjdh bymlạ ạlsmạ
 dynj dwnj mjdh bymlạ ạlsmạ
 Ding dong the festive bells now chime
 Ding dong to tell it's Christmas time
 The angels sing their anthems ring
 Good news to all mankind
 So come along with the joyful song
 Let glory fill the sky
 Ding dong let glory fill the sky</lyrics>
<title>dqt ạ̉jrạs ạlʿyd</title>
